  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Paquis is on a bed and breakfast basis.</p>
<p>Each morning a varied continental breakfast buffet is served between 7:30-9:30am. In<span>cludes savoury options such as boiled eggs, ham, cheese and sausages, while the sweet options includes pastries, cereals, bread, butter, jam, yoghurt, fromage frais, compotes and preserves.</span></p>
<p><span>The hotel offers a variety of "Bocaux du Bistrot" (bistro jars) made with a range of fresh ingredients. Choose from a range of soups, appetisers, main dishes and desserts - whether you fancy a snack or a sweet treat, there'll be something on offer. Pay locally. </span></p>
<p>There is a good selection of restaurants close by for the evenings, whether you fancy Savoyard specialities or pizza, there is something for everyone. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
