<p><strong>Fantastic location overlooking the Lake in Tignes le Lac.</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>From the hotel walk less than a minute down to the piste and ski down to the Rosset chair or Tovière gondola. The ski school meeting point and nursery slopes are by these two lifts. </li>
<li>There are some good restaurants and bars less than 2 minutes' walk from the hotel and the main shops of Tignes Le Lac are 5 minutes' walk away</li>
</ul>
